form.longName: PhenX PX070201 - Cumulative Lifetime Physical Activity
form.preferredDefinition: The selected protocol assesses strenuous and moderate physical activities and exercise at various stages of life. Respondents are asked to estimate the average amount of time each week and the average number of months each year that they spend doing strenuous and moderate exercise.

form.preferredDefinition: This protocol assesses exposure to environmental tobacco smoke (ETS) during childhood and in adulthood at home, at work, and in social settings. The duration of ETS exposure is collected in hours per day and years for each setting. In addition, there is a question about current ETS exposure.

headerInstruction.text: We are interested in your exposure to smoke from other people's cigarettes and tobacco products.

question.questionText: Were you exposed to smoke from other people's cigarettes or tobacco products during Childhood at home? (exposure_smoke_childhood)
For how many hours per day? (exposure_smoke_childhood_hours)
For how many hours per day? (exposure_smoke_childhood_hours_coded)
Were you exposed to smoke from other people's cigarettes or tobacco products during Adulthood at home? (exposure_smoke_adulthood_home)
For how many hours per day? (exposure_smoke_adulthood_home_hours)
For how many hours per day? (exposure_smoke_adulthood_home_hours_coded)
Were you exposed to smoke from other people's cigarettes or tobacco products during Adulthood at work? (exposure_smoke_adulthood_work)
For how many hours per day? (exposure_smoke_adulthood_work_hours)
For how many hours per day? (exposure_smoke_adulthood_work_hours_coded)

Were you exposed to smoke from other people's cigarettes or tobacco products during In social settings such as bars, restaurants, bowling alleys, bingo halls, and friends' homes? (exposure_smoke_social_settings)
For how many hours per day? (exposure_smoke_social_settings_hours)
For how many hours per day? (exposure_smoke_social_settings_hours_coded)
At the present time, how many hours per day are you exposed to the smoke of others? (exposure_smoke_present_time_hours)

protocol.preferredDefinition: This protocol assesses exposure to environmental tobacco smoke (ETS) during childhood and in adulthood at home, at work, and in social settings. The duration of ETS exposure is collected in hours per day and years for each setting. In addition, there is a question about current ETS exposure.

form.longName: PhenX PX070401 - Exogenous Female Hormone Use
form.preferredDefinition: Female respondents self-report the use of estrogen and progesterone, including the duration and dose.

question.questionText: Have you ever taken estrogen (female hormones") for symptoms of menopause (the change of life) or for other reasons?" (ever_taken_estrogen)

validValue.meaningText: Yes, and I am currently taking estrogens
validValue.description: Yes, and I am currently taking estrogens

validValue.meaningText: Yes, but I am no longer taking estrogens
validValue.description: Yes, but I am no longer taking estrogens

question.questionText: The most frequently used estrogen is oral Premarin®. Have you ever taken Premarin® by mouth (as pills)? (ever_premarin)
At what age did you first take Premarin®? (premarin_age_first)
At what age did you last take Premarin®? (premarin_age_last)
How many years in total did you take Premarin® (exclude those periods when you temporarily stopped)? (premarin_years)

Five commonly used doses of Premarin® can be distinguished by the color of the pill. Please indicate any you have ever used and the one you used for the longest period. Green (0.3 mg). (premarin_dose_green)

Five commonly used doses of Premarin® can be distinguished by the color of the pill. Please indicate any you have ever used and the one you used for the longest period. Brown/Red (0.625 mg). (premarin_dose_brown_red)

Five commonly used doses of Premarin® can be distinguished by the color of the pill. Please indicate any you have ever used and the one you used for the longest period. White (0.9 mg). (premarin_dose_white)

Five commonly used doses of Premarin® can be distinguished by the color of the pill. Please indicate any you have ever used and the one you used for the longest period. Yellow/Orange (1.25 mg). (premarin_dose_yellow_orange)

Five commonly used doses of Premarin® can be distinguished by the color of the pill. Please indicate any you have ever used and the one you used for the longest period. Purple (2.5 mg). (premarin_dose_purple)
Have you ever used estrogen other than Premarin® pills? Estrogen by mouth? (ever_estrogen_by_mouth)
Have you ever used estrogen other than Premarin® pills? Estrogen by injection? (ever_estrogen_by_injection)
Have you ever used estrogen other than Premarin® pills? Estrogen by patch or implant? (ever_estrogen_by_patch_implant)
Have you ever used estrogen other than Premarin® pills? Estrogen vaginal cream or suppository? (ever_estrogen_by_cream_suppository)
At what age did you first use estrogens other than Premarin® pills? (estrogen_except_premarin_age_first)
At what age did you last use estrogens other than Premarin® pills? (estrogen_except_premarin_age_last)
How many years in total did you take estrogens other than Premarin® pills (exclude any time when you temporarily stopped)? (estrogen_except_premarin_years)

Sometimes another type of female hormone, progesterone (or progestin) is given for symptoms of menopause either alone or in combination with estrogen. The most frequently used progestin is Provera® (medroxyprogestoerone acetate). Have you ever used progesterone or a progestin? (ever_progesterone_progestin)

validValue.meaningText: Provera® and another type of progestin
validValue.description: Provera® and another type of progestin

question.questionText: At what age did you first take progesterone or a progestin? (progesterone_progestin_age_first)
At what age did you last take progesterone or a progestin? (progesterone_progestin_age_last)
How many years in total did you take progesterone or a progestin (excluding any time when you temporarily stopped)? (progesterone_progestin_years)
If you used Provera®, what was your usual dose? (provera_dose)
When using progestin or progesterone, for how many days each month would you usually take it? (progesterone_progestin_days)
